FINGER

Finger allows you to see some information provided by other players.  You can
set the info from the main menu.  To view a player's finger information use:

   finger <name>

Information about your e-mail address is viewable only by high level immortals,
so if you wish to make it visible to other players, put it in your plan as
well.
#
DEATH

Death is a very nasty thing. It usually means you didnt kill that mob or ran
into a rather nasty trap. Death here is a bit different, you lose your exp
like normal BUT you will also lose levels/mana/hps down to the max level you
can have with your new exp total (note, this can happen by fleeing alot as well)
You will not gain any new practices until you reach your old level but anything
you had already learned will stay practiced (just not useable until your the
correct level again).
Currently when you die it is impossible to have your corpse looted by PLAYERS
but mobs are able to if they are smart enough (most are). The only times when
this isnt true is if you have CHOOSEN or if you have given CONSENT to someone

 SEE ALSO: CONSENT, CHOOSE
#
STORAGE STORAGE_CHARACTERS

The bank will hold items for you now. It wont hold any item worth less than
1k gold and you will be charged for their service at what would be normal
renting prices if we charged rent. To deposit an item you type deposit <item>
to list items type list and to withdraw you type withdraw <item>. You are
charged once a real day or when you withdraw an item you are charged for part
of the day (based on deposite time).

please note STORAGE CHARACTERS are *NOT* allowed and will be deleted if you
are caught. You will also face banishment for some time and if you do it to
much you will face deletion as well.

 SEE ALSO: MULTIPLAYING

