#
RECHARGER

Recharger will let other PC's act like a battery for you to get mana from.
You can only cast this on someone who has given you their CONSENT and who
hasnt been used for a recharge for the last 48 ticks. There is a small
detriment to the battery, they will lose 20 hps for the 48 hour duration.
This is not perminate. You can only use this on a PC within 40 levels of
you.

#
