"FAERIE"

Faerie fire adversely affects the targets armor class by 1 point, making
the target easier to hit.

Faerie fog causes all invisible creatures in the room (who do not fail
their save) to become visible.
#
MINOR

Components  : black pearl
Minor creation creates an object, either a raft, a bag, a sword, a shield,
a barrel or a piece of bread.
ex:
   cast 'minor' raft

#
"TRUE SIGHT"
Components  : 

True sight allows you to see hidden creatures, and invisible creatures,
it is a (temporary) cure for blindness, and allows you to see in the
dark, or will soon.

