INFO
Gives you some useful hints and information about the game.
#
USERS

     Tells you who is logged on to the game, and where they are playing
from.  The output can be formatted using the following flags:

         Usage: users [-c] [-t] [-l] [-h] [-i] [-c]
         Example: users -i -c -h
                 -c : condensed
                 -l : sorted by level
                 -h : sorted by host
                 -n : sorted by name
                 -i : immortals only
                 -t : totals only

