Value[1]: Max Charges (1..X)
Value[2]: Charges Left
Value[3]: Which spell in staff (see list somewhere around the end of file)

#
ITEM_WEAPON

ITEM_WEAPON (5)
Value[0]: Not Used
Value[1]: Number of dice to roll for damage
Value[2]: Size of dice to roll for damage
Value[3]: The weapon type. Type is one of:

         NUMBER  CATEGORY   Message type
            2  : Slash         "whip/whips"
            3  : Slash         "slash/slashes"

            6  : Bludgeon      "crush/crushes"
            7  : Bludgeon      "pound/pounds"

           11  : Pierce        "pierce/pierces"

          New types will be added as needed.

    case 0  : w_type = TYPE_SMITE; break;
    case 1  : w_type = TYPE_STAB;  break;
    case 2  : w_type = TYPE_WHIP; break;
    case 3  : w_type = TYPE_SLASH; break;
    case 4  : w_type = TYPE_SMASH; break;
    case 5  : w_type = TYPE_CLEAVE; break;
    case 6  : w_type = TYPE_CRUSH; break;
    case 7  : w_type = TYPE_BLUDGEON; break;
    case 8  : w_type = TYPE_CLAW; break;
    case 9  : w_type = TYPE_BITE; break;
    case 10 : w_type = TYPE_STING; break;
    case 11 : w_type = TYPE_PIERCE; break;
